{"title":"最短母串问题","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2999","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>给定n个字符串（S1,S2,...,Sn），要求找到一个最短的字符串T，使得这n个字符串（S1,S2,...,Sn）都是T的子串。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>输入第一行是一个正整数n，表示给定的字符串的个数。以下的n行，每行有一个全由大写字母组成的字符串。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>输出中只有一行，为找到的最短的字符串T。在保证最短的前提下，如果有多个字符串都满足要求，那么必须输出按字典序排列的第一个。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2 <br>ABCD<br>BCDABC</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>ABCDABC</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>n&lt;12，且每个字符串的长度不超过50。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}